2. Certification Authority Reservation

NovaFuse-EGP-VS is a certification instrument.

Only NovaFuse Technologies, or entities explicitly authorized in writing by NovaFuse,
may:

(a) issue official NovaFuse certificates;
(b) operate a certification service based on NovaFuse-EGP-VS;
(c) represent verification results as "NovaFuse-Certified" or equivalent.

Execution of the software does not grant certification authority.

